data.description: Country Charmer!  This old house has endless possibilities!  This 1700+ sq ft 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bath 1900s home offers a Large Rocking Chair Front Porch and a large side screened porch to enjoy the beautiful countryside.  Large living room with hardwood floors, masonry fireplace w/gas logs. Gourmet Kitchen w/Custom Cabinets, granite counter tops, gas range, commercial size fridge, kitchen bar all open to dining with custom built-ins. Large Master suite w/walk in closet and private bath (large tile shower) custom cabinets. Guest bedroom with half bath.  Full guest bath in the hall. Outside check out this awesome barn, additional outbuilding, stalls for horses or cows, fenced pasture and garden area.  Come take a look today!
